reviewText: This is an excellent DVD pack with 6 DVDs. The stories are wonderful for all the family. It is a time and money saver to buy this set. I Love these programs and everyone asks for more. But I have been looking and I think this collectors pack contains all of them. (All seasons)
I had to return it as it did not work. Dvd 1 and 2 had lot of scratches. Also this has newer version which I did not want
